      • addTagSuggestionProvider

        public void addTagSuggestionProvider(TagSuggestionProvider provider)
        Adds a new TagSuggestionProvider provider. If an TagSuggestionProvider with the same alias already exists the given one will replace this one.
        Parameters:
        provider - The provider.

      • findTagSuggestions

        public Collection<TagSuggestion> findTagSuggestions(TagStoreType type,
                                                    Collection<String> tagSuggestionProviderAliases,
                                                    Collection<String> tagSuggestionAliases,
                                                    boolean assignedTagsOnly,
                                                    Map<String,Object> filters,
                                                    QueryParametersParameterNameProvider nameProvider,
                                                    Locale locale)
        Searches for tags with the specified filters.
        Parameters:
        type - Type of the TagStore to filter for.
        tagSuggestionProviderAliases - The aliases of providers to use for searching. If null or empty all providers will be used.
        tagSuggestionAliases - Aliases of tag suggestions to consider. If null or empty all suggestions will be used.
        assignedTagsOnly - if true only suggestions of tags that are already assigned to Communote entities have to be be returned. If false, the tags don't have to be assigned to Communote entities.
        filters - The filters to use.
        nameProvider - The name provider to use.
        locale - The locale to use for filtering localized tags.
        Returns:
        List of suggestions.

      • getTagSuggestionConfigurations

        public List<TagSuggestionConfiguration> getTagSuggestionConfigurations(TagStoreType type,
                                                                       boolean assignedOnly)
        Parameters:
        type - a tag store type to only consider providers that support that type. Can be null to allow all types.
        assignedOnly - If true, only providers that can return suggestions for tags that are already assigned to Communote entities will be considered
        Returns:
        A list of all TagSuggestionConfigurations.
